API Server
==========

* python-setuptools (python_distribute in Arch Linux)
* flask (easy_install flask)
* mysql server 
* flask.ext.sqlalchemy (easy_install flask-sqlalchemy)
* python-mysqldb (mysql_python on Arch Linux)
* pyredis (easy_install redis) [optional]
* redis server [optional, needed for realtime support]

CLI consumer
=============

* requests (easy_install requests)

Pyntas bridge
=============

* node.js
* node_redis (npm install redis)
* socket.io (npm install socket.io)
